=== Getting the files that have a matroska container and have subtitles ===
{{{
#> ls -l ~/dmxfs/video_x-matroska/text_plain/files
lrwxr-xr-x 1 root root 0 1970-01-01 01:00 00079515 -> ~/media/Planet.51.720p.Bluray.x264-CBGB.mkv
}}}

